{"tid":1303961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明 點解而家18區搞遊行都要質疑？","createTime":"2019-07-10T13:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:48:22.000Z","uid":21262,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c24439103870d294e9ad1366dec3562811a97a24","tid":1303961,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"有人話失焦：但其實將軍澳區+港島西既遊行都講左係將個重擺去五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n至於作用：屯門遊行已經睇得出 已經即刻逼到賣港建制做野搶光環<br />\n黎緊紅土遊行、上水因爲水貨客、大陸團客影響哂日常生活 有屯門遊行借鏡可以睇得出係有用<br />\n<br />\n搶人數：28號兩個遊行撞左 咪各有各搞囉 <strong>等班狗忙到仆街都好呀</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔係就係遍地開花既最好例子咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">不過我同意 應該集中一日搞返個大既港島區聚返民意人氣</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多得一班狗同林奠撥火加持 先一劑過激發到咁多民怨係呢一兩個月爆哂出黎 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同埋我地香港人keep住做野 正正就係同政府講 我地香港人冇咁善忘架DLLM</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場係持久戰！我係冇咁快放棄！想出一分力既街站、傳單、連儂牆、遊行、課金、抵制TVB等等都已經做到野 <br />\n<br />\n利申9UP"},{"pid":"ac0d50ddab2be8ad15c85aaf97f0c9b013068eeb","tid":1303961,"uid":21002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"係講比人知民建聯同政府有幾癈<br />\n10年冇做過野 而家到人地踢到埋黎先識做"},{"pid":"f02ca66494a7fa837605eaaf03c59aad9b8691ac","tid":1303961,"uid":21262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VZdyim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VZdyim.png&h=556b2078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BC486Dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBC486Dn.png&h=2ec7c720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1X08nbH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2